title: 'merging Python dictionaries (from *within* a dictionary) :  nwrap with **'
pid: 88971f77-9463-446d-a07b-9ff1d0f601df
body: |2-
  PITFALL: Later keys clobber earlier ones.
  { **{1:2, 3:4},
    5:6,    # NOTE: key-val pairs can be mixed in like this.
    **{7:8} }
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
